			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Gamescom 2017: It’s all fun and games until black hats step in</h1>
<div class="excerpt">ESET researchers have discovered a new sneaky malware threat named Joao, targeting gamers worldwide.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
                <div class="wls-author with-avatar">
